title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Tianyuan plans 400 mln yuan worth of bonds issue
text:
Sept 21 Shenzhen Tianyuan Dic Information Technology Co Ltd
* Says plans to issue up to 400 million yuan ($62.82 million) worth of bonds with maturities of up to 5 years
